Torrential rains in KwaZulu-Natal have caused severe damage to homes, infrastructure and businesses. LADYSMITH - Torrential rains in KwaZulu-Natal have caused severe damage to homes, infrastructure and businesses. Heavy rains pounded Ladysmith over the weekend causing flooding in various parts of the town. READ: Officials to determine cost of damage in flood-hit Ladysmith At least one person has been confirmed dead. eNCA's Mawande Kheswa has more.